               <msContents>
                  <summary>Ff. 1r-62r:Antiphonary for the Fast of Lent, ጾመ፡ ድጓ፡. F. 61v: Note of ownership. Ff. 62r-64r: Various secondary notes and texts, including Lucky and Unlucky Days of the Year, ጽንዕት፡ ወጽንጽንት፡, </summary>
